highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Jaipur. Kesariya is the highest at #4.
Jhoome Jo Pathaan by Vishal-Shekhar, Arijit Singh, Sukriti Kakar, Vishal Dadlani, Shekhar Ravjiani, and Kumaar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Jaipur, up 36 spots at #11.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Jaipur the longest, at 67 weeks straight.
